{"tid":367544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"已經盡量唔諗佢 但都係訓唔著","createTime":"2017-08-20T21:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T03:49:48.000Z","uid":114635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40af7736e2fbac46cedaf682631236a48e87d2b7","tid":367544,"uid":114635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T21:38:09.000Z","msg":"鐘意左個女仔年半 基本上情侶會做既野都做晒但係一直都冇一齊到 今年年頭佢問我係咪好鐘意佢我答係 佢就叫我等佢今年努力搵夠錢就一齊 上個月仲叫我等埋佢半年 點知早2日同我講話佢同第二個一齊左 叫我快d搵返個女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話其實今年2月之後就唔鐘意我 點解要呃我又拖住我咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所有朋友都叫我唔好再搵佢 但真係驚自己會忍唔住會搵佢 又有朋友話過一排試下好似普通朋友咁搵佢睇下佢有咩反應再算 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹想上黎發洩下"},{"pid":"d61baf7ccaf9adb735ee511abdde4bab9b44c2d9","tid":367544,"uid":20538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T21:58:20.000Z","msg":"工具人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02280965dbfd0011146d5734a013bfa21dd1f7ec","tid":367544,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T22:10:25.000Z","msg":"臭雞一隻"},{"pid":"38c4dbdf3dc525f907756dbfd39976aa71e68511","tid":367544,"uid":114635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:10:29.000Z","msg":"就黎已經忍唔住好想搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817ded1ea719ac26c7c20d6667be4faefe0b4df6","tid":367544,"uid":124824,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:15:19.000Z","msg":"咪犯賤啦 仲想搵翻佢啊？<br />\n佢當你水泡咋 以為可以做到人男朋友？<br />\n睇唔睇到係佢呃鳩你話2月仲鍾意你叫你等佢<br />\n結果收咗好人卡，仲想搵翻對方？<br />\n留翻啲尊嚴比自己啦"},{"pid":"2fa6516cf1ba753c1750fdf1be036bf9fa2c79b4","tid":367544,"uid":118420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s